        <abstract> 
<p>Is disappointed at high price, 7s 6d, being considered for the cheap edition of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [6th ed.]. Has been told that, in Lancashire, workmen club together to buy the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Little chance that <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi> will be done this autumn.</p> 
